long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Redirects JoJo Wikia/Fandom requests to jojowiki.com
Redirects JoJo Wikia/Fandom requests to 'JoJo's Bizarre Encyclopedia' automatically to help ensure that you are always viewing the most up-to-date information possible. 

This extension will work for any links so long as you use Google Chrome by default. You may also temporarily pause the extension in order to view pages on the Fandom site.
